text: Theodor Körner (April 23, 1873 - January 4, 1957) was the president of Austria from 1951-1957. Previously he was mayor and governor of Vienna from 1945 to 1951. ==Other websites== Category:1873 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Governors of Austrian States Category:Mayors Category:Presidents of Austria
title: Theodor Körner
